      <p>You may stop using DhanRakshak at any time by uninstalling the app from your device.</p>
      <p>You can delete all your data (local and cloud) at any time from within the app. For detailed instructions on how to delete your account and all associated data, see our <a href={`${base}delete-account/`}>Account & Data Deletion</a> page.</p>
